{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2890060/extras/Header_Abilities.png?t=1739192707\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2890060/extras/Abilities.gif?t=1739192707\" /><br><strong>Be prepared for anything as the monsters abilities keep evolving and changing!</strong><br>The monster player has limited control over their next ability so they will also have to think quickly to make the best use of them!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2890060/extras/Header_MonsterInvisible.png?t=1739192707\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2890060/extras/InvisibleInShadows.gif?t=1739192707\" /><br><strong>Hide in the shadows and kill your prey one by one!</strong><br>Stalk your prey from a distance and stay as close as possible without being seen. Then strike before they have time to react!<br><br>You're completely invisible in the shadows. Avoid light at all cost!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2890060/extras/Header_Gadgets.png?t=1739192707\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2890060/extras/Gadgets.gif?t=1739192707\" /><br>You have various improvised weapons and gadgets at your disposal to locate and defend from the monster. <br>Use the right tool at the right time to shift the tides!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2890060/extras/Header_HumanObjective.png?t=1739192707\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2890060/extras/HumanObjective.gif?t=1739192707\" /><br>Work together to survive and banish the monster once and for all!<br>Don't forge